# upd-skill

Update Claude Code skills from GitHub to your project.

```bash
uvx upd-skill <username>/<skill-name>
```

To fetch from upd.dev:

```bash
uvx upd-skill upd.dev/<username>/<skill-name>
```

See [agent-resources](https://upd.dev/skills/agent-skills-project) for full documentation.
